      "comment": "TRIZLA (1) is an accomplished sprinter with a great record at the short dashes. Kept coming to fill the minor placings over 350m at this track (20.29) in a Grade 5. Form at the trip excellent including four wins. Has a strong record from box 1, including two wins. Can measure up this time. RUSHFORTH BAZ (2) has been in the frame at his last two runs, most recently when second (20.25) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Expected to do much better this time. IMOGENE PASS (6) box seated off the lead and kept coming to win (22.49) at Gosford in Grade 5 over 388m. Makes plenty of appeal on the back of that last-start win. OLLING (4) racing over this distance brings the best out in him.",
